      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Kingman Approx Overview\nThis dashboard breaks the current queueing formula into exact and approximate parts.\n\n- Exact broker-side inputs: `q_rabbitmq_*`\n- Reliable service-capacity inputs: `free_slots_*`, `in_flight_*`, `q_total_*`, `lambda_*`\n- Approximate timing / queueing outputs: `approx_e_s_*`, `approx_mu_*`, `approx_rho_*`, `approx_score_*`\n\nCurrent `telephon` timing `_sum/_count` are reconstructed from rolling averages, so all **Approx** series are operational approximations only.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Formula Caveats",
      "type": "text"
    },
